snippet.title: ComputerCraft
snippet.description:
In game, programmable, redstone capable computers for Minecraft.
Download and installation instructions are viewable at http://www.minecraftforum.net/topic/892282-100-computercraft/

The song used in this video is "Fun with Science" by Akira the Don.
Check out his music at http://www.akirathedon.com
